rawContent:
My soul it’s full
To brim in pain
Demon forces
Are at it again
Swirling doubts 
Within my head, 
Planting whispers 
I’d be better off dead 
Angels attempt to beam demons w/ bright light. Yet.
I’m not sure who’ll win this fight. 

Lucella Thetis  

#poetry #depression #lonlyness

Some differences between #anxiety and #depression

With depression, physical changes often involve a slowing down, such as feeling tired. 

Anxiety, by contrast, usually involves a speeding up of physical changes, such as a racing heart, jumpiness, or cold sweat.

#mentalhealth
